{"tid":50161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁錮驚魂】「禁錮出租女友」 22歲男虛構禁室培慾被捕","createTime":"2016-12-22T08:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T23:53:47.000Z","uid":426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a23221e2fc3a0f482bf82faee476ca14b307e3e","tid":50161,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"警方昨日接獲多個報案，指發現有人在本月15日在網上討論區張貼文章及多張相片，相片中的女子懷疑被襲擊及非法禁錮。網絡安全及科技罪案調查科人員經深入調查後，相信沒有相關案件發生，於昨日晚上約7時在長沙灣一單位，拘捕一名22歲姓賴本地男子，涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦及浪費警力。被捕男子現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n被捕青年上周起於網上論壇發文，內容指不滿一名「出租女友」收錢後，拒絕提供性服務及拍攝淫照，其後將少女「起底」，並威逼她到住所留宿，否則通知其學校及父母她任出租女友一事。<br />\n<br />\n被捕青年上載多張女子遭手銬鐵鏈禁錮及凌辱的照片，繪形繪聲描述數度找少女到住所凌辱的過程。雖然原文有加上「頭盔：此post內容純屬虛構」，但事件仍引起網友不安，擔憂屬實，於是轉載至高登討論區，事件疑幻疑真，網上關注，多名網友先後報警。<br />\n<br />\n網友Eason表示，在瀏覽高登得悉事件，「好不安、唔尋常」，他認為疑犯所說有太多細節，並涉及違法行為，疑犯更指到新年後才會放過少女，認為事態嚴重，於是前往深水埗警署報警。<br />\n<br />\n[img<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161222/280pix/1482369551_55e5.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2F280pix%2F1482369551_55e5.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=fa1afcf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161222/280pix/1482369551_55e5.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n被捕青年於網上論壇聲稱禁錮一名十多歲少女，並上載多張凌辱照片(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161222&amp;guid=56077235&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161222%26guid%3D56077235%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cbbb96e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161222%26guid%3D56077235%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=bbff484f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161222&amp;guid=56077235&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b798bff042edb185c6a323cb967823cc4e9df404","tid":50161,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/162232_9be6834a269db845fb1d0ab11a2f513b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F162232_9be6834a269db845fb1d0ab11a2f513b.jpg&h=29e7c815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d7752528f8da9b671aceb15d1bd46c06a23e78","tid":50161,"uid":1205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"網上虛構禁室培慾惹恐慌，網友Eason好不安報警，警拘22歲網民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/49698/page/15?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/49698/page/15?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb38cb75fd763a40c0b701beb28efade211c7099","tid":50161,"uid":17211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"明顯係早洩畀料人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610edf3b58e26decc16adffcc1e02304a25495bf","tid":50161,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明顯係早洩畀料人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個原post喺new3lunch呀，醒未呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}